The wait is over! Ever since the conclusion of Avatar: The Last Airbender, its millions of fans have been hungry for more--and its finally here!

This series of digests rejoins Aang and friends for exciting new adventures, beginning with a faceoff against the Fire Nation that threatens to throw the world into another war, testing all of Aangs powers and ingenuity!

* The continuation of The Last Airbender Tv Series and the link to its upcoming sequel, Legend of Korra!

